<section>
  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:800px;">
    <span class="lbl">FAQ</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Common questions about<br/>fractional CMO pricing.</h2>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">How much does a fractional CMO cost per month?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Typically $3,000–$20,000 per month depending on scope, hours, and seniority. Most B2B companies in the $5M–$50M range land between $6,000 and $12,000/month for a meaningful engagement with real accountability.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">What hourly rate does a fractional CMO charge?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Rates range from $150–$400/hour depending on experience and specialization. Most don't work pure-hourly — they package into monthly retainers for predictability. If you're being quoted hourly, ask for a monthly package instead.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">Do fractional CMOs take equity?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Some do, most don't — especially at $5M+ revenue. Equity makes sense at pre-seed/seed stages where cash is tight. For companies with revenue, cash arrangements are cleaner. If offered, typical grants are 0.1–0.5% vesting over 2–4 years.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">Is a fractional CMO worth the cost?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">For most B2B companies at $5M–$50M, yes — if the alternative is no marketing leadership or an expensive full-time hire. Run the ROI math: even a 15% improvement in marketing-sourced pipeline usually pays back within 60 days at typical close rates and deal sizes.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-q">How long do fractional CMO contracts last?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Most engagements start with a 3-month pilot, then move to rolling monthly. Average engagement length is 12–18 months. Companies graduate out when they hire full-time marketing leadership — which is the intended outcome for healthy, growing businesses.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" style="background:#050D05;">
  <div class="sec-inner" style="max-width:680px;">
    <span class="lbl">Get a Transparent Quote</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Tell us your situation. We'll give you<br/>an honest starting-from number.</h2>
    <p class="sub">No fake discovery calls that are really sales pitches. A 15-minute conversation to understand your scope and give you a real number.</p>
    <div id="contact-form">
      <div class="form-grid">
        <div>
          <label class="form-label">First Name</label>
          <input class="input-field" type="text" id="first_name" placeholder="Jane" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="form-label">Last Name</label>
          <input class="input-field" type="text" id="last_name" placeholder="Smith" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">Work Email</label>
        <input class="input-field" type="email" id="email" placeholder="jane@company.com" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">Company</label>
        <input class="input-field" type="text" id="company" placeholder="Acme Inc." />
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label class="form-label">What's your biggest AI or marketing challenge right now?</label>
        <textarea class="input-field" id="gain" placeholder="Trying to decide between fractional CMO and full-time hire, need to understand real cost/scope..." style="min-height:100px;resize:vertical;"></textarea>
      </div>
      <input type="hidden" id="source" value="fractional-cmo-cost" />
      <button class="btn-p" id="submit-btn" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;" onclick="submitForm()">Get a Transparent Quote →</button>
      <p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:#4A6A4A;margin-top:0.75rem;text-align:center;">We respond within one business day with a real number.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="thankyou" id="thankyou">
      <div class="thankyou-h">Expect a real answer.</div>
      <p style="color:#8FAF8F;">We'll be in touch within one business day with transparent pricing for your situation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<GlobalFooter />

<script>
async function submitForm() {
  const btn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
  btn.textContent = 'Sending...'; btn.disabled = true;
  try {
    await fetch('/api/lead-capture', { method: 'POST', headers: {'Content-Type':'application/json'}, body: JSON.stringify({ first_name: document.getElementById('first_name').value, last_name: document.getElementById('last_name').value, email: document.getElementById('email').value, company: document.getElementById('company').value, gain: document.getElementById('gain').value, source: document.getElementById('source').value }) });
    document.getElementById('contact-form').style.display = 'none';
    document.getElementById('thankyou').style.display = 'block';
  } catch(e) { btn.textContent = 'Get a Transparent Quote →'; btn.disabled = false; }
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
